Dovecot (open source IMAP and POP3 server)

Dovecot is an open source IMAP and POP3 server for Linux/UNIX-like
systems, written with security primarily in mind. Although it's
written in C, it uses several coding techniques to avoid most of the
common pitfalls.

Home: http://www.dovecot.org

======================================================================
Requires:
cyrus-sasl 
postgresql 
